{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Raise VED road tax for cars registered before April 2017 to at least \u00a3195 a year",
        "additional_details": "We think it's unfair to pay less tax for a car just because it's a bit older.\r\nThe road network in the UK needs improvement and the lack of funds to maintain and build new roads is becoming an issue.\r\nEveryone needs to pay their way into the system if you plan to use the public road network.\r\n",
        "background": "We believe that we all need to pay for road tax in a fair and consistent way.\r\nPre 2017 vehicles only pay \u00a320-\u00a330 if their emissions are low.\r\nIn our view, the minimum road tax should be \u00a3195 for all vehicles.",
